description:
Thanks to the work Ash did in getting Gumshoos and Yungoos to help with the Rattata and Raticate problem on Melemele Island, Officer Jenny made a new friend and partner with Gumshoos.
Rotom Pokédex noted that it is a tenacious and patient Stakeout Pokémon and that it had 99.7 percent compatibility with Officer Jenny.
name: Dekagoos (Junsaa)
